          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1696855960349-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and carrot are beginning to soften, add the<strong> diced potato</strong>, <strong>sliced mushrooms</strong> and <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> (save the rest for later!) to the pan</p><p>Cook for 1 min, then add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
